quarks.runtime.etiao.graph.model

Class GraphType

  • java.lang.Object
    • quarks.runtime.etiao.graph.model.GraphType

  • public class GraphType
extends java.lang.Object
    A generic directed graph of vertices, connectors and edges.

    The graph consists of VertexType objects, each having 0 or more input and/or output EdgeType objects. EdgeType objects connect an output connector to an input connector.

    A vertex has an associated Oplet.
